@node "comment" " Comment about scrolling"
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| 8. Comment about scrolling                                                 |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                            |
|  I made it possible to choose wich way the wall should scroll. I.e if the  |
| new messages should arrive at the top or the bottom.                       |
| However this function was too slow so I removed. Perphaps I'll make a      |
| faster function for this and the future and it will then be added.         |
|                                                                            |
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
